==English==
===Noun===
'''curry'''

# a mixture of [[spice]]s, usually including [[turmeric]], also known as ''[[curry powder]]''
#: when made into a paste with a liquid, such as water or milk, known as ''[[curry paste]]''.
# a sauce whose principal flavoring is curry powder.
# an Asian-style [[dish]] or [[stew]] made with curry.

====Synonyms====
*[[ruby murray]] (''rhyming slang'')

